# Maktab Telegram Bot — To'liq qo'llanma

## Imkoniyatlar
- Ro'yxatdan o'tish (7 bosqich)
- Fanlar tanlash (tugmalar orqali)
- Google Sheets ga avtomatik saqlash
- Admin tasdiqlash / rad etish
- Foydalanuvchiga bildirishnoma
- Statistika
- Bekor qilish buyrug'i
- Noto'g'ri xabarga javob

## Buyruqlar
| Buyruq | Kim uchun | Vazifasi |
|--------|-----------|---------|
| /start | Hammaga | Bosh menyu |
| /yordam | Hammaga | Yordam |
| /bekor | Hammaga | Ro'yxatni bekor qilish |
| /statistika | Faqat admin | Ariza statistikasi |
| /arizalar | Faqat admin | Oxirgi 10 ariza |

## O'rnatish

### 1. Bot yaratish
- @BotFather → /newbot → TOKEN oling

### 2. Admin ID olish
- @userinfobot → /start → ID oling

### 3. Google Sheets sozlash
1. console.cloud.google.com ga kiring
2. Yangi loyiha yarating
3. Google Sheets API + Google Drive API ni yoqing
4. Service Account yarating → JSON kalit yuklab oling
5. Google Sheets da yangi jadval oching
6. Jadval URL dan ID oling
7. Jadvalni Service Account emailiga Editor sifatida ulashing

### 4. Render deploy
1. render.com → GitHub bilan kiring
2. New → Background Worker
3. GitHub repo ulang
4. Environment Variables:
   - BOT_TOKEN
   - ADMIN_CHAT_ID
   - GOOGLE_CREDENTIALS (JSON faylning ichidagi hamma matn)
   - SPREADSHEET_ID
5. Deploy!
